ErrorProfileBuilder

To test with a sample example:
python errorProfileBuilder.py -b sample_example/chr21chr22chrM.sorted.bam -i sample_example/chr21chr22chrM.sorted.bam.bai -r sample_example/chr21chr22chrM.fa.gz


Input:
Sorted BAM, Sorted BAM index, genomic reference
BAM files must be aligned to the genomic reference given as input
For more details: python errorProfileBuilder.py --help


Output:
error_profile.basic : file with the chance of a base being wrong
error_profile.detailed : file with the chance of a base being wrong + the chance of each specific error